A Form Three Student From Busijo Secondary School In Samia Busia County Was Murdered In Cold Blood As Her Friend Was Sexually Assaulted After They Were Attacked By Unknown People.According To Her Aunt The Two Who Hail From From Nasira In Matayos Constituency Were Attacked On Their Way Home From A Disco Matanga In The Neighborhood Over The Weekend.Speaking From Her Bed At Busia Referral Hospital Where She Is Admitted, The Girl Narrated The Ordeal Saying She Was Hit With Blunt Object By Unknown People On Her Way Home Together With The Deceased Who Was Slashed By A Panga And Died On The Spot